---
title: Fig Jam-Bouree Pork Cutlets with Mashed Potatoes & Zucchini
description: Na na na na na na na nana / Na na na na nana / Gettin’ figgy with it. Fig jam, that is! Here, we’ve paired it with balsamic vinegar and rich chicken stock to bring you a pan sauce that’s equal parts sweet, tangy, and savory. In other words, it’s the perfect topping for pan-seared pork cutlets. On the side, there’s creamy mashed potatoes and roasted zucchini, making this a square meal that totally rocks. This fun and fruity recipe will get your tastebuds dancing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fig-jam-bouree-pork-cutlets-3b1806fc.jpg
